sub_title: Helping NGOs in DACH to increase impact with digitalization
summary: As an Account Executive at Salesforce.org, the social impact center of Salesforce, I support nonprofit organisations in Germany, Austria and Switzerland to reach their goals and maximise their impact with digitalisation and technology. Through identifying needs, priorities and challenges of nonprofits, we can help transform businesses and simplify business operations as well as enable a more data-driven approach within organisations, ultimately leading to greater social impact.
